Yes, but it's a pity that it's not canon. After all, according to canon, amulets are not divided into red and blue. They only have different chain colors, but the amulets are the same. 
It's a pity that the anime's author decided to take some things from the reboot. After all, the anime could have been much more interesting and better without the 2013 reboot.
